# Vercel deploys api/*.js (serverless functions) + public/ (static) only.
# These are Render/local-dev-only or collection-pipeline-only files that
# don't belong in the Vercel bundle — server.js in particular must NOT be
# picked up as an accidental duplicate Express function (Vercel auto-detects
# it via the "express" dependency otherwise, doubling up with api/*.js).
server.js
collector/
requirements.txt
render.yaml
reports/raw/
